{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"Graphic Basics 3 着色器","date":1525119270000,"slug":"Graphic-Basics-3","content":"<p>着色器：<a href=\"https://learnopengl.com/Getting-started/Shaders\">https://learnopengl.com/Getting-started/Shaders</a></p>\n<h2>加载 Shader 文件</h2>\n<p>使用 webpack 官方的 raw-loader 来加载</p>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  test<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\"><span class=\"token special-escape escape\">\\.</span><span class=\"token group punctuation\">(</span>glsl<span class=\"token alternation keyword\">|</span>vs<span class=\"token alternation keyword\">|</span>fs<span class=\"token alternation keyword\">|</span>txt<span class=\"token group punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token anchor function\">$</span></span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  use<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'raw-loader'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\">vShader</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./shaders/uv.vs\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\">fShader</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./shaders/texture.fs\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>找到了<a href=\"http://stack.gl/packages/#stackgl/glslify\">glslify</a>, 但因为它的维护不活跃了，所以没有使用。</p>"},"prev":{"slug":"Graphic-Basics-2","title":"Graphic Basics 2 变换与坐标系统","date":1524859455000},"next":{"slug":"ray-casting-selecting","title":"在WebGL中使用射线选择模型","date":1534877523000}},"__N_SSG":true}